{"surah":{"number":64,"name":"التغابن","englishName":"At-Taghabun","englishTranslation":"The Mutual Disillusion","ayahCount":18},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:25.945Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"Whatever is in the heavens and whatever is on the earth is exalting Allah. To Him belongs dominion, and to Him belongs [all] praise, and He is over all things competent.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُسَبِّحُ","english":"Glorifies","translit":"yusabbiḥu","root":"سبح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","english":"[to] Allah","translit":"lillahi","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"whatever","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and whatever","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَهُ","english":"For Him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_001_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْمُلْكُ","english":"(is the) dominion","translit":"l-mul'ku","root":"ملك","audio":"wbw/064_001_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَلَهُ","english":"and for Him","translit":"walahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_001_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْحَمْدُ ۖ","english":"(is) the praise","translit":"l-ḥamdu","root":"حمد","audio":"wbw/064_001_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"And He","translit":"wahuwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_001_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"(is) on","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_001_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/064_001_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/064_001_018.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"قَدِيرٌ","english":"All-Powerful","translit":"qadīrun","root":"قدر","audio":"wbw/064_001_019.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"It is He who created you, and among you is the disbeliever, and among you is the believer. And Allah, of what you do, is Seeing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"(is) the One Who","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَلَقَكُمْ","english":"created you","translit":"khalaqakum","root":"خلق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَمِنكُمْ","english":"and among you","translit":"faminkum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَافِرٌۭ","english":"(is) a disbeliever","translit":"kāfirun","root":"كفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمِنكُم","english":"and among you","translit":"waminkum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّؤْمِنٌۭ ۚ","english":"(is) a believer","translit":"mu'minun","root":"أمن"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_002_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"of what","translit":"bimā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_002_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","english":"you do","translit":"taʿmalūna","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/064_002_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"بَصِيرٌ","english":"(is) All-Seer","translit":"baṣīrun","root":"بصر","audio":"wbw/064_002_012.mp3"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"He created the heavens and earth in truth and formed you and perfected your forms; and to Him is the [final] destination.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","english":"He created","translit":"khalaqa","root":"خلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ","english":"with truth","translit":"bil-ḥaqi","root":"حقق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَصَوَّرَكُمْ","english":"and He formed you","translit":"waṣawwarakum","root":"صور"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَحْسَنَ","english":"and made good","translit":"fa-aḥsana","root":"حسن"},{"position":7,"arabic":"صُوَرَكُمْ ۖ","english":"your forms","translit":"ṣuwarakum","root":"صور"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَإِلَيْهِ","english":"and to Him","translit":"wa-ilayhi","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_003_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","english":"(is) the final return","translit":"l-maṣīru","root":"صير","audio":"wbw/064_003_010.mp3"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"He knows what is within the heavens and earth and knows what you conceal and what you declare. And Allah is Knowing of that within the breasts.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُ","english":"He knows","translit":"yaʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَعْلَمُ","english":"and He knows","translit":"wayaʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"تُسِرُّونَ","english":"you conceal","translit":"tusirrūna","root":"سرر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"تُعْلِنُونَ ۚ","english":"you declare","translit":"tuʿ'linūna","root":"علن"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_004_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","english":"(is) All-Knowing","translit":"ʿalīmun","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/064_004_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"بِذَاتِ","english":"of what","translit":"bidhāti","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_004_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلصُّدُورِ","english":"(is in) the breasts","translit":"l-ṣudūri","root":"صدر","audio":"wbw/064_004_015.mp3"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Has there not come to you the news of those who disbelieved before? So they tasted the bad consequence of their affair, and they will have a painful punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Has not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَأْتِكُمْ","english":"come to you","translit":"yatikum","root":"أتي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَبَؤُا۟","english":"(the) news","translit":"naba-u","root":"نبأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(of) those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieved","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلُ","english":"before","translit":"qablu","root":"قبل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَذَاقُوا۟","english":"So they tasted","translit":"fadhāqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَبَالَ","english":"(the bad) consequence","translit":"wabāla","root":"وبل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَمْرِهِمْ","english":"(of) their affair","translit":"amrihim","root":"أمر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَلَهُمْ","english":"and for them","translit":"walahum","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"عَذَابٌ","english":"(is) a punishment","translit":"ʿadhābun","root":"عذب"},{"position":13,"arabic":"أَلِيمٌۭ","english":"painful","translit":"alīmun","root":"ألم"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"That is because their messengers used to come to them with clear evidences, but they said, \"Shall human beings guide us?\" and disbelieved and turned away. And Allah dispensed [with them]; and Allah is Free of need and Praiseworthy.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِأَنَّهُۥ","english":"(is) because","translit":"bi-annahu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَت","english":"had","translit":"kānat","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَّأْتِيهِمْ","english":"come to them","translit":"tatīhim","root":"أتي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رُسُلُهُم","english":"their Messengers","translit":"rusuluhum","root":"رسل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ","english":"with clear proofs","translit":"bil-bayināti","root":"بين"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَقَالُوٓا۟","english":"but they said","translit":"faqālū","root":"قول"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَبَشَرٌۭ","english":"Shall human beings","translit":"abasharun","root":"بشر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَهْدُونَنَا","english":"guide us","translit":"yahdūnanā","root":"هدي"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَكَفَرُوا۟","english":"So they disbelieved","translit":"fakafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَتَوَلَّوا۟ ۚ","english":"and turned away","translit":"watawallaw","root":"ولي"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَّٱسْتَغْنَى","english":"And can do without them","translit":"wa-is'taghnā","root":"غني","audio":"wbw/064_006_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_006_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_006_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"غَنِىٌّ","english":"(is) Self-sufficient","translit":"ghaniyyun","root":"غني","audio":"wbw/064_006_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"حَمِيدٌۭ","english":"Praiseworthy","translit":"ḥamīdun","root":"حمد","audio":"wbw/064_006_018.mp3"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Those who disbelieve have claimed that they will never be resurrected. Say, \"Yes, by my Lord, you will surely be resurrected; then you will surely be informed of what you did. And that, for Allah, is easy.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"زَعَمَ","english":"Claim","translit":"zaʿama","root":"زعم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوٓا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَّن","english":"never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُبْعَثُوا۟ ۚ","english":"will they be raised","translit":"yub'ʿathū","root":"بعث"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/064_007_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بَلَىٰ","english":"Yes","translit":"balā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_007_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَرَبِّى","english":"by my Lord","translit":"warabbī","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/064_007_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"لَتُبْعَثُنَّ","english":"surely you will be raised","translit":"latub'ʿathunna","root":"بعث","audio":"wbw/064_007_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"then","translit":"thumma","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_007_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"لَتُنَبَّؤُنَّ","english":"surely you will be informed","translit":"latunabba-unna","root":"نبأ","audio":"wbw/064_007_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"of what","translit":"bimā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_007_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"عَمِلْتُمْ ۚ","english":"you did","translit":"ʿamil'tum","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/064_007_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"وَذَٰلِكَ","english":"And that","translit":"wadhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_007_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"for","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_007_018.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_007_019.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"يَسِيرٌۭ","english":"(is) easy","translit":"yasīrun","root":"يسر","audio":"wbw/064_007_020.mp3"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"So believe in Allah and His Messenger and the Qur'an which We have sent down. And Allah is Acquainted with what you do.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَـَٔامِنُوا۟","english":"So believe","translit":"faāminū","root":"أمن"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَرَسُولِهِۦ","english":"and His Messenger","translit":"warasūlihi","root":"رسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلنُّورِ","english":"and the Light","translit":"wal-nūri","root":"نور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِىٓ","english":"which","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَنزَلْنَا ۚ","english":"We have sent down","translit":"anzalnā","root":"نزل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_008_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"of what","translit":"bimā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_008_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","english":"you do","translit":"taʿmalūna","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/064_008_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"خَبِيرٌۭ","english":"(is) All-Aware","translit":"khabīrun","root":"خبر","audio":"wbw/064_008_011.mp3"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"The Day He will assemble you for the Day of Assembly - that is the Day of Deprivation. And whoever believes in Allah and does righteousness - He will remove from him his misdeeds and admit him to gardens beneath which rivers flow, wherein they will abide forever. That is the great attainment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَجْمَعُكُمْ","english":"He will assemble you","translit":"yajmaʿukum","root":"جمع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِيَوْمِ","english":"for (the) Day","translit":"liyawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْجَمْعِ ۖ","english":"(of) the Assembly","translit":"l-jamʿi","root":"جمع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(will be the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/064_009_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلتَّغَابُنِ ۗ","english":"(of) mutual loss and gain","translit":"l-taghābuni","root":"غبن","audio":"wbw/064_009_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_010.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنۢ","english":"believes","translit":"yu'min","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/064_009_011.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_009_012.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَيَعْمَلْ","english":"and does","translit":"wayaʿmal","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/064_009_013.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحًۭا","english":"righteous deeds","translit":"ṣāliḥan","root":"صلح","audio":"wbw/064_009_014.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"يُكَفِّرْ","english":"He will remove","translit":"yukaffir","root":"كفر","audio":"wbw/064_009_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"عَنْهُ","english":"from him","translit":"ʿanhu","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"سَيِّـَٔاتِهِۦ","english":"his evil deeds","translit":"sayyiātihi","root":"سوأ","audio":"wbw/064_009_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"وَيُدْخِلْهُ","english":"and He will admit him","translit":"wayud'khil'hu","root":"دخل","audio":"wbw/064_009_018.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"(to) Gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن","audio":"wbw/064_009_019.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","english":"flow","translit":"tajrī","root":"جري","audio":"wbw/064_009_020.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_021.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","english":"underneath it","translit":"taḥtihā","root":"تحت","audio":"wbw/064_009_022.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ","english":"the rivers","translit":"l-anhāru","root":"نهر","audio":"wbw/064_009_023.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","english":"abiding","translit":"khālidīna","root":"خلد","audio":"wbw/064_009_024.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_025.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"أَبَدًۭا ۚ","english":"forever","translit":"abadan","root":"أبد","audio":"wbw/064_009_026.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_009_028.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلْفَوْزُ","english":"(is) the success","translit":"l-fawzu","root":"فوز","audio":"wbw/064_009_029.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلْعَظِيمُ","english":"the great","translit":"l-ʿaẓīmu","root":"عظم","audio":"wbw/064_009_030.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"But the ones who disbelieved and denied Our verses - those are the companions of the Fire, abiding eternally therein; and wretched is the destination.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"But those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieved","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَكَذَّبُوا۟","english":"and denied","translit":"wakadhabū","root":"كذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَآ","english":"[in] Our Verses","translit":"biāyātinā","root":"أيي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"those","translit":"ulāika","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبُ","english":"(are the) companions","translit":"aṣḥābu","root":"صحب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","english":"(of) the Fire","translit":"l-nāri","root":"نور"},{"position":8,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","english":"abiding forever","translit":"khālidīna","root":"خلد"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۖ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَبِئْسَ","english":"And wretched is","translit":"wabi'sa","root":"بأس","audio":"wbw/064_010_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","english":"the destination","translit":"l-maṣīru","root":"صير","audio":"wbw/064_010_012.mp3"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"No disaster strikes except by permission of Allah. And whoever believes in Allah - He will guide his heart. And Allah is Knowing of all things.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَصَابَ","english":"strikes","translit":"aṣāba","root":"صوب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّصِيبَةٍ","english":"disaster","translit":"muṣībatin","root":"صوب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِإِذْنِ","english":"by (the) permission","translit":"bi-idh'ni","root":"أذن"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۗ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_011_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنۢ","english":"believes","translit":"yu'min","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/064_011_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_011_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"يَهْدِ","english":"He guides","translit":"yahdi","root":"هدي","audio":"wbw/064_011_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"قَلْبَهُۥ ۚ","english":"his heart","translit":"qalbahu","root":"قلب","audio":"wbw/064_011_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_011_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"بِكُلِّ","english":"of every","translit":"bikulli","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/064_011_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/064_011_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۭ","english":"(is) All-Knowing","translit":"ʿalīmun","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/064_011_018.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And obey Allah and obey the Messenger; but if you turn away - then upon Our Messenger is only [the duty of] clear notification.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَطِيعُوا۟","english":"So obey","translit":"wa-aṭīʿū","root":"طوع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَطِيعُوا۟","english":"and obey","translit":"wa-aṭīʿū","root":"طوع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولَ ۚ","english":"the Messenger","translit":"l-rasūla","root":"رسل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَإِن","english":"but if","translit":"fa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_012_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَوَلَّيْتُمْ","english":"you turn away","translit":"tawallaytum","root":"ولي","audio":"wbw/064_012_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","english":"then only","translit":"fa-innamā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_012_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"upon","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_012_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"رَسُولِنَا","english":"Our Messenger","translit":"rasūlinā","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/064_012_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْبَلَـٰغُ","english":"(is) the conveyance","translit":"l-balāghu","root":"بلغ","audio":"wbw/064_012_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْمُبِينُ","english":"clear","translit":"l-mubīnu","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/064_012_012.mp3"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Allah - there is no deity except Him. And upon Allah let the believers rely.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"al-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَآ","english":"(there is) no","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهَ","english":"god","translit":"ilāha","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"هُوَ ۚ","english":"Him","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَعَلَى","english":"And upon","translit":"waʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_013_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_013_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَلْيَتَوَكَّلِ","english":"let put (their) trust","translit":"falyatawakkali","root":"وكل","audio":"wbw/064_013_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ","english":"the believers","translit":"l-mu'minūna","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/064_013_010.mp3"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"O you who have believed, indeed, among your wives and your children are enemies to you, so beware of them. But if you pardon and overlook and forgive - then indeed, Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(you) who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوٓا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِكُمْ","english":"your spouses","translit":"azwājikum","root":"زوج"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَأَوْلَـٰدِكُمْ","english":"and your children","translit":"wa-awlādikum","root":"ولد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَدُوًّۭا","english":"(are) enemies","translit":"ʿaduwwan","root":"عدو"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَّكُمْ","english":"to you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَٱحْذَرُوهُمْ ۚ","english":"so beware of them","translit":"fa-iḥ'dharūhum","root":"حذر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"But if","translit":"wa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_014_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"تَعْفُوا۟","english":"you pardon","translit":"taʿfū","root":"عفو","audio":"wbw/064_014_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَتَصْفَحُوا۟","english":"and overlook","translit":"wataṣfaḥū","root":"صفح","audio":"wbw/064_014_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"وَتَغْفِرُوا۟","english":"and forgive","translit":"wataghfirū","root":"غفر","audio":"wbw/064_014_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"then indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_014_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_014_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"غَفُورٌۭ","english":"(is) Oft-Forgiving","translit":"ghafūrun","root":"غفر","audio":"wbw/064_014_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌ","english":"Most Merciful","translit":"raḥīmun","root":"رحم","audio":"wbw/064_014_019.mp3"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Your wealth and your children are but a trial, and Allah has with Him a great reward.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","english":"Only","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلُكُمْ","english":"your wealth","translit":"amwālukum","root":"مول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَوْلَـٰدُكُمْ","english":"and your children","translit":"wa-awlādukum","root":"ولد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِتْنَةٌۭ ۚ","english":"(are) a trial","translit":"fit'natun","root":"فتن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"and Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_015_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥٓ","english":"with Him","translit":"ʿindahu","root":"عند","audio":"wbw/064_015_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَجْرٌ","english":"(is) a reward","translit":"ajrun","root":"أجر","audio":"wbw/064_015_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَظِيمٌۭ","english":"great","translit":"ʿaẓīmun","root":"عظم","audio":"wbw/064_015_009.mp3"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"So fear Allah as much as you are able and listen and obey and spend [in the way of Allah]; it is better for your selves. And whoever is protected from the stinginess of his soul - it is those who will be the successful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱتَّقُوا۟","english":"So fear","translit":"fa-ittaqū","root":"وقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱسْتَطَعْتُمْ","english":"you are able","translit":"is'taṭaʿtum","root":"طوع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱسْمَعُوا۟","english":"and listen","translit":"wa-is'maʿū","root":"سمع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَطِيعُوا۟","english":"and obey","translit":"wa-aṭīʿū","root":"طوع"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَأَنفِقُوا۟","english":"and spend","translit":"wa-anfiqū","root":"نفق"},{"position":8,"arabic":"خَيْرًۭا","english":"(it is) better","translit":"khayran","root":"خير"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لِّأَنفُسِكُمْ ۗ","english":"for yourselves","translit":"li-anfusikum","root":"نفس"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_016_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"يُوقَ","english":"is saved","translit":"yūqa","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/064_016_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"شُحَّ","english":"(from the) greediness","translit":"shuḥḥa","root":"شحح","audio":"wbw/064_016_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"نَفْسِهِۦ","english":"(of) his soul","translit":"nafsihi","root":"نفس","audio":"wbw/064_016_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"then those","translit":"fa-ulāika","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_016_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"هُمُ","english":"[they]","translit":"humu","root":"","audio":"wbw/064_016_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْمُفْلِحُونَ","english":"(are) the successful ones","translit":"l-muf'liḥūna","root":"فلح","audio":"wbw/064_016_017.mp3"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"If you loan Allah a goodly loan, He will multiply it for you and forgive you. And Allah is Most Appreciative and Forbearing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِن","english":"If","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُقْرِضُوا۟","english":"you loan","translit":"tuq'riḍū","root":"قرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"(to) Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَرْضًا","english":"a loan","translit":"qarḍan","root":"قرض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حَسَنًۭا","english":"goodly","translit":"ḥasanan","root":"حسن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُضَـٰعِفْهُ","english":"He will multiply it","translit":"yuḍāʿif'hu","root":"ضعف"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَيَغْفِرْ","english":"and will forgive","translit":"wayaghfir","root":"غفر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَكُمْ ۚ","english":"you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/064_017_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"شَكُورٌ","english":"(is) Most Appreciative","translit":"shakūrun","root":"شكر","audio":"wbw/064_017_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"حَلِيمٌ","english":"Most Forbearing","translit":"ḥalīmun","root":"حلم","audio":"wbw/064_017_013.mp3"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Knower of the unseen and the witnessed, the Exalted in Might, the Wise.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَـٰلِمُ","english":"(The) Knower","translit":"ʿālimu","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبِ","english":"(of) the unseen","translit":"l-ghaybi","root":"غيب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلشَّهَـٰدَةِ","english":"and the witnessed","translit":"wal-shahādati","root":"شهد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعَزِيزُ","english":"the All-Mighty","translit":"l-ʿazīzu","root":"عزز"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","english":"the All-Wise","translit":"l-ḥakīmu","root":"حكم"}]}]}
